  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110133008426\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110133008426\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp; \r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 32px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 20px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 32px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 20px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">건강을 위한 식습관 10가지~</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\"><a class=\"con_link\" name=\"#1976269987\" target=\"_blank\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3c5971cbd274f177.jpg\" width=\"135\" height=\"180\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 135px; rheight: 180px\" id=\"20120302_229/isuhani_1330686358051iqapr_JPEG/%BE%C6%C4%A7%B9%E4%BB%F3.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A470582A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3c5971cbd274f177.jpg\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">1 . 아침은 꼭 먹는다.</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">아침을 먹으면 기초대사량이 높아져 살이 찌지 않는 체질로 변한다는 사실~</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">아침식사는 빠를수록 좋아요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">오전 7시부터 늦어도 오전 9시 이전에 식사하되 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">포만감이 느껴지지 안는 양의 70%만 먹는 것이 중요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">위에 부담이 되지 않도록 일어나자마자</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">물이나 차 한잔으로 위 운동을 촉진시키고 20~30분 후 아침식사를</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">해주는 것이 꼭 지켜야할 좋은 습관.</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">아침에 식욕이 없어 밥이 먹기 힘들다면 식사전</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">가벼운 스트레칭이나 운동을 해 보는것도 좋은 방법이구요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">식용 상승은 물론 잠자는 동안 내려간 체온을 올려주어 다이어트에 도움이 되요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">2 . 같은 음식 2~3회 식탁에 올리지 않기</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">신선한 재료로 먹기 직전 만들어 먹는 음식이 영양가가 높고 맛있어요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">국이나 반찬을 한번에 많이 만들어 먹으면 짜지고</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">기름지게 되어 건강에 물론 좋을 순 없겠죠</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">귀찮더라도 식사 때마다 먹을 양만 조리해 신선하게 즐기는</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">하나의 방법이죠</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">3 . 3~4시간 간격으로 음식 섭취하기</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">건강을 위해서는 하루 총 몇 칼로리를 먹느냐보다 몇 번에 나누어</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">어떤 영양소를 섭취하는지가 더 중요해요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">하루 섭취해야 할 에너지를 간식으로 분산하면 공복감 없이 과식을</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">막을 수 있고 또한 비만 예방과 치료에 효과적인 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">방법중 하나의 식습관이죠</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">적은 양의 간식을 자주 섭취하면 급격한 혈당상승을 막아</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">당뇨병 위험을 줄일수 있어요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">실제 병원에서는 당뇨환자에게 식사량을 줄이는 대신 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">적은양의 간식을 자주 섭취하는</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">식이요법을 권장하고 있어요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">그렇듯이 자주 나눠먹는 것도 건강을 위한 하나의 식습관이에요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5bda61e50cfac7b9.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"120\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 180px; rheight: 120px\" id=\"20120302_143/isuhani_1330686405777jIxsK_JPEG/%C4%C3%B7%AF%C7%AA%B5%E5.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A470582A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5bda61e50cfac7b9.jpg\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><a class=\"con_link\" name=\"#1976269988\" target=\"_blank\"></a></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">4 . 컬러푸드 먹기</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">컬러푸드의 인기는 계속 높아지고 있는데요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">끼니마다 블랙푸드, 레드푸드, 그린푸드, 옐로푸드, 화이트푸드로</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">이루어진 5가지 컬러의 음식을 골고루 갖춰 먹으면</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">우리 건강에 벨런스를 유지하는 좋은 식습관이에요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/241b539b6b1da2b4.jpg\" width=\"141\" height=\"180\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 141px; rheight: 180px\" id=\"20120302_5/isuhani_1330686493873koldu_JPEG/%BB%FD%BC%B1.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A470582A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/241b539b6b1da2b4.jpg\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><a class=\"con_link\" name=\"#1976269991\" target=\"_blank\"></a></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">5 . 생선종류 많이 먹기</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">풍부한 영양소와 맛을 동시에 책임지는 생선 역시 각광받는 다이어트 식품이자</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">아이들 키 크는데 좋은 음식이지요~</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">양질의 단백질과 건강에 이로운 비타민D, 아미노산 등을</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">다량 함유하고 있는 생선은 육류보다는 낮은 칼로리와 담백한 맛이 특징</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">다이어트 할때는 지방 함량이 높은 등 푸른 생선과 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">붉은살 생선보다는 흰살생선이 더 효과적이에요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">겨울 제철 생선인 생태 명태는 특히 다이어트 생선으로 손 꼽히고</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">있어요 건강을 위해 매번 식단에 흰살생선을 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">올려 건강을 지키는 식습관중 하나예요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">6 . 먹을 음식 미리 준비하기</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">점심이나 간식으로 먹으면 좋을 견과류 스낵이나 건강음료</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">신선한 샐러드 등을 미리 준비하면 배가</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">고플 때 칼로리 높은 군것질꺼리를 피할수 있는 식습관중 하나예요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">조금만 더 신경써서 샐러드를 준비하여</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">다이어트에도 도움이 되고 건강한 몸을 위해 공을 더 들여보자구요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5f92b2c297f0b979.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"139\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 180px; rheight: 139px\" id=\"20120302_89/isuhani_13306866000767pRBm_JPEG/%C7%F6%B9%CC%B9%E4.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A470582A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5f92b2c297f0b979.jpg\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><a class=\"con_link\" name=\"#1976269992\" target=\"_blank\"></a></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">7 . 갈색 식품 고르기</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">우리 음식중 주식이 밥이죠. 이 밥중에도 백미보다는 현미가 좋은거</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">다들 아시죠, 희밀보다는 호밀이 좋구요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">까칠한 식감 때문에 피하기 쉬운데요 소화가 잘 안되는 느낌이</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">들어서 꺼린다면 잘못된 생각!!!</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">이 식품들이 소화가 안 되는 이유는 탄수화물 속에 먹어도 살이 안 찌는</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">특별한 성분이 들어있기 때문이에요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">우리 식탁에도 흰색보다는 갈색 즉 잡곡을 많이 섭취하는 것이</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">건강을 지키는 식습관이에요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/54a32fcdf4a016de.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"119\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 180px; rheight: 119px\" id=\"20120302_291/isuhani_1330686623228cTLuM_JPEG/%B0%FA%BD%C41.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A470582A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/54a32fcdf4a016de.jpg\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\"><a class=\"con_link\" name=\"#1976269996\" target=\"_blank\"></a>8 . 과식하지 않기</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">과식이 나쁘다는 건 누구나 다 아시는 사실,</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">그러나 맛있는 음식 앞에 “조금만 먹어야지”라는 다짐은 물거품이</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">된걸 다들 아시죠..메인 메뉴를 먹기 전 음료를 한 잔</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">마시거나 과일을 먼저 먹으면 어느 정도 과식을 막을 수 있는 방법이에요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">무심코 먹게 되는 메뉴 중엔 칼로리가 만만치 않은 것이 많으니</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">자주 먹는 식사 메뉴의 칼로리를 알아 두는것도</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">우리 몸을 지키는 하나의 식습관이에요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">9 . 똑똑한 오일과 향신료 선택하기</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">기름이라고 우리 몸에 다 헤로운 것은 아니에요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">요리 전에 몸에 좋은 오일, 가령 올리브오일이나 해바라기씨유 같은</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">식물성기름은 우리 몸에 이롭다고 해도 과언이 아닌데요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">또한 소금이나 설탕대신 허브와 향신료를 대체하여 사용하는 것도</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">좋은 식습관중 하나이에요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120302_91/isuhani_1330686642728AXMll_JPEG/%B9%B0.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"180\" height=\"122\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 180px; rheight: 122px\" id=\"20120302_91/isuhani_1330686642728AXMll_JPEG/%B9%B0.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A470582A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120302_91/isuhani_1330686642728AXMll_JPEG/%B9%B0.jpg?type=w3\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><a class=\"con_link\" name=\"#1976269997\" target=\"_blank\"></a></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 15px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">10 . 물 자주 마시기</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">흔히 다이어트 하는 방법중 제일 중요한 식습관이라고 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">다들 물 마니 마시세요~ 라고 하잖아요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">그와 같이 물은 우리 몸에 중요한 부분을 차지하고 있어요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">“배고프다”는 느낌을 갈증의 첫 번째 신호인데요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">대분분의 사람들은 “배고픔”을 오해하고 있어요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">모든 세포는 효율적으로 기능하기 위해 수분을 필요로 해요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">얼굴에만 미스트 뿌려 수분 채우지 마시구요 틈틈이 물을</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">마셔서 최소 하루 2L정도의 물을 섭취하는</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '휴먼엑스포'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\">식습관을 가져야 해요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '바탕'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '바탕'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '한컴바탕'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: '한컴바탕'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: '한컴바탕'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 13px\"><a href=\"http://blog.naver.com/world7488/150131791981\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"con_link\">http://blog.naver.com/world7488/150131791981</a>&nbsp;- 출처</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
